These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
House: gothic-revival, tower, farmhouse
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, cranberry, pepper
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, police-officer, dressmaker
City: liverpool, paris, edinburgh
1. the person eating cranberry is the tower house##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far left##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the chef is the person eating pepper##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the farmhouse house is the person eating pepper##1
7. the dressmaker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| House      | farmhouse  | gothic-revival       | tower   |
| Food          | pepper | cauliflower | cranberry |
| Job         | chef  | dressmaker | police-officer    |
| City   | edinburgh | liverpool       | paris      |

