.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, potato, radish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, ambient, indie
City: paris, marseilles, boston
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, tennis, skiing
1. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is skiing is the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Food          | pear      | potato  | radish        |
| Music-Genre         | indie | ambient | funk |
| City   | paris | marseilles | boston       |
| Sport           | skiing     | tennis     | badminton      |

