.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different pets are kept: rat, goat, bird
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, mango, orange
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, mauve, red
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the person eating orange is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person who likes red is in the middle##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person eating orange##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Pet      | goat    | rat        | bird |
| Food           | mango    | orange | pineapple    |
| Color   | pink | red             | mauve  |
| Transport     | train     | bus                | subway  |

