.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
City: hannover, san-francisco, colone
3 different pets are kept: frog, ferret, hedgehog
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, horror, western
3 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, go
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is the person playing go##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| City          | san-francisco    | colone  | hannover      |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | frog | ferret |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | horror  | drama     |
| Game   | canasta | monopoly    | go      |

