.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different games are played: chess, poker, go
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, may, october
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, musical, superhero
There 3 different types of food: tomato, zucchini, strawberry
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person playing chess##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person playing go##1
4. the person playing go is on the far left##1
5. the person eating tomato is the person playing chess##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Game         | go | chess     | poker   |
| Birthday           | october       | may   | august     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | documentary | superhero |
| Food           | strawberry      | tomato         | zucchini  |

