The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
3. the person playing billiard is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who likes apricot##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
6. the person playing whist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Game       | billiard            | canasta      | whist  |
| Birthday         | july | september | june |
| Color         | ivory               | apricot | mauve |
| Transport   | roller             | ship       | bus      |

