1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
6. the person eating peas is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Game           | backgammon | whist         | scrabble |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | martial-arts | mystery     |
| Food   | pumpkin   | peas       | grapes     |
| Beverage           | water    | coffee         | iced-tea        |

