.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, traveling, singing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, dahlia, daisy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, prince, game
1. the game-smoker is the fan of gospel##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who growslily##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
5. the game-smoker is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Hobby      | singing    | traveling | camping |
| Flower   | dahlia | lily     | daisy     |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | gospel        | folk        |
| Cigar           | prince    | game         | alhambra     |

