.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, water
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, british, dutch
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, pomegranate, lemon
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person drinking water is the british##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
6. the dutch is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Beverage         | coffee | mirinda | water   |
| Nationality           | dutch     | spanish    | british   |
| Food   | pomegranate         | lemon    | zucchini   |
| Sport         | cricket       | sailing | badminton |

