3 different games are played: billiard, scrabble, domino
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, reggae, disco
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bus, motorbike
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday    | december | september     | november      |
| Game        | billiard | scrabble       | domino |
| Music-Genre       | reggae | hip-hop | disco  |
| Transport   | bus    | airplane   | motorbike  |

