The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, zombie, sports
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | soy-milk   | sprite  |
| Transport          | train   | roller | snowmobile   |
| Game   | poker      | snooker      | billiard    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | crime    | sports |

