.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, dahlia, lily
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, lilycher
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, board-games
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, dog
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the lilycher is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person who growslily is the owner of the bird##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Flower      | dahlia         | lily     | sunflower     |
| Job           | lawyer        | lilycher | journalist |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing        | board-games   | collecting    |
| Pet         | dog | bird   | ferret |

