.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, orchid, aconite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, swisher, fonseca
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, snooker
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, surfing, water-polo
1. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
6. the game-smoker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Flower          | aconite     | orchid    | bellflower    |
| Cigar         | game | fonseca | swisher     |
| Game   | backgammon  | scrabble      | snooker        |
| Sport         | handball   | surfing   | water-polo |

 